oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Walton family
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group picture of the Walton family standing in front of their barn in Rugby. Pictured are Robert Walton (1841-1907), his wife Elizabeth "Lizzie" Taylor Walton (1849-1933), and their children William Taylor Walton (1877-1958), Esther Walton Keen (1878-1968) and John Kimber Walton (1883-1899).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Families; Barns
